(144, 'widget_image_text_widget', 'a:8:{i:3;a:15:{s:10:"responsive";b:1;s:8:"image_id";i:129;s:14:"image_position";s:10:"above_text";s:5:"title";s:22:"Criminal Investigation";s:4:"text";s:274:"If you are charged with a crime, not only is having a good attorney important, but also, it is equally important in having a private investigator with the right kind of experience and knowledge. In some instances, private investigators have never worked in law enforcement. ";s:9:"text_type";s:5:"plain";s:9:"link_type";s:4:"page";s:15:"link_custom_url";s:0:"";s:12:"link_page_id";i:7;s:11:"link_target";s:4:"same";s:4:"size";s:9:"thumbnail";s:17:"size_custom_width";i:220;s:18:"size_custom_height";i:140;s:11:"image_align";s:6:"center";s:10:"text_align";s:7:"justify";}i:6;a:15:{s:10:"responsive";b:1;s:8:"image_id";i:39;s:14:"image_position";s:10:"above_text";s:5:"title";s:27:"Corp & Residential Security";s:4:"text";s:281:"Whether you are a Fortune 500 company, a small local business or a home owner, a comprehensive security plan is of the upmost importance in today&#039;s times. Recent trends in legislation such as a Senate Bill in California, are charging employers with the safety and security... ";s:9:"text_type";s:5:"plain";s:9:"link_type";s:4:"page";s:12:"link_page_id";i:15;s:15:"link_custom_url";s:0:"";s:11:"link_target";s:4:"same";s:4:"size";s:9:"thumbnail";s:17:"size_custom_width";i:220;s:18:"size_custom_height";i:140;s:11:"image_align";s:4:"none";s:10:"text_align";s:7:"justify";}i:7;a:15:{s:10:"responsive";b:1;s:8:"image_id";i:40;s:14:"image_position";s:10:"above_text";s:5:"title";s:10:"Infidelity";s:4:"text";s:289:"Parker Investigations understands the sensitive nature of these types of investigations and the need in keeping this information secure and confidential. Our professional team of prior law enforcement personnel knows the importance of obtaining the evidence you need properly and legally. ";s:9:"text_type";s:5:"plain";s:9:"link_type";s:4:"page";s:15:"link_custom_url";s:0:"";s:12:"link_page_id";i:9;s:11:"link_target";s:4:"same";s:4:"size";s:9:"thumbnail";s:17:"size_custom_width";i:220;s:18:"size_custom_height";i:140;s:11:"image_align";s:4:"none";s:10:"text_align";s:7:"justify";}i:8;a:15:{s:10:"responsive";b:1;s:8:"image_id";i:41;s:14:"image_position";s:10:"above_text";s:5:"title";s:19:"Police Use of Force";s:4:"text";s:302:"These types of investigations usually involve both criminal and civil matters. After having investigated numerous “Officer Use of Force” cases for several law enforcement agencies, we are able to review the evidence in these types of cases and are able to make a determination, based on the facts. ";s:9:"text_type";s:5:"plain";s:9:"link_type";s:4:"page";s:15:"link_custom_url";s:0:"";s:12:"link_page_id";i:11;s:11:"link_target";s:4:"same";s:4:"size";s:9:"thumbnail";s:17:"size_custom_width";i:220;s:18:"size_custom_height";i:140;s:11:"image_align";s:4:"none";s:10:"text_align";s:7:"justify";}i:9;a:15:{s:10:"responsive";b:1;s:8:"image_id";i:42;s:14:"image_position";s:10:"above_text";s:5:"title";s:25:"Background Investigations";s:4:"text";s:292:"Whether you are a director of human resources at your company needing to hire employees or someone wanting to enter the online dating sites wanting to meet someone for a date, you need to know who that person really is. A comprehensive background check can reveal possible criminal activity. ";s:9:"text_type";s:5:"plain";s:9:"link_type";s:4:"page";s:15:"link_custom_url";s:0:"";s:12:"link_page_id";i:13;s:11:"link_target";s:4:"same";s:4:"size";s:9:"thumbnail";s:17:"size_custom_width";i:220;s:18:"size_custom_height";i:140;s:11:"image_align";s:4:"none";s:10:"text_align";s:7:"justify";}i:10;a:15:{s:10:"responsive";b:1;s:8:"image_id";i:190;s:14:"image_position";s:10:"above_text";s:5:"title";s:18:"Statement Analysis";s:4:"text";s:281:"This area of investigation involves the scientific analysis of both written and verbal statements made by witnesses, victims and suspects. PARKER has received training and certification in Scientific Content Analysis from one of the most renowned developers of this field of study.";s:9:"text_type";s:5:"plain";s:9:"link_type";s:4:"page";s:15:"link_custom_url";s:0:"";s:12:"link_page_id";i:177;s:11:"link_target";s:4:"same";s:4:"size";s:9:"thumbnail";s:17:"size_custom_width";i:220;s:18:"size_custom_height";i:140;s:11:"image_align";s:4:"none";s:10:"text_align";s:4:"none";}i:11;a:15:{s:10:"responsive";b:1;s:8:"image_id";i:191;s:14:"image_position";s:10:"above_text";s:5:"title";s:27:"Death Investigation Reviews";s:4:"text";s:269:"Parker has been involved in the investigation of over 300 death cases over his career. They range from natural, suicide, homicide, accidental and undetermined. If one of your family members has died and you have questions about the circumstances surrounding the death..";s:9:"text_type";s:5:"plain";s:9:"link_type";s:4:"page";s:15:"link_custom_url";s:0:"";s:12:"link_page_id";i:183;s:11:"link_target";s:4:"same";s:4:"size";s:9:"thumbnail";s:17:"size_custom_width";i:220;s:18:"size_custom_height";i:140;s:11:"image_align";s:4:"none";s:10:"text_align";s:7:"justify";}s:12:"_multiwidget";i:1;}', 'yes'),
